          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As someone who has studied here for 13+ years do not enroll in this is school . It's living off past glory just handful of exceptional teachers . Most of the teaching staff is incompetent to be teachers they have inflated egos, they just have degrees .Some of them do know their subject but have no idea how to teach . And the condition of the buildings is just awful . Extra curricular activities have no structure or proper focus on developing young talents . I hope no other student has to go though this hell hole of a school",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
