            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My school. Studied here from class 1 to class 12 and frankly speaking, this school helped shape my personality and helped me attain good habits and valuable skills. Yeah, it is true that the buildings lack playgrounds. But finding a plot to build a new school in a well-connected( in terms of frequent and cheap public transport) old urban area in the 21st century and having enough plot area to leave ample open spaces do not go hand in hand.\nOverall, my school gave me everything i needed as a kid and i'm proud of her.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
