            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Unruly staff at the gate.\nGross behavior and vulgar language.\nI had parked my car in front of their main gate unknowingly..I was at fault there i agree ..I would obviously moved the car somewhere else ..but the way the staff dealt with this was really uninviting and something never expected from an educational institution.\nI seriously don't want to Judge this esteem institution on the behavior I witnessed but they've left me out of words.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
